<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,326,152,176]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">Etymology</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
The species name is a Latin adjective (
<emphasis box="[775,963,152,176]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">liniger, -ra, -rum</emphasis>
= wearing linen).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
